high_descs: Turn left and make your way over to the fridge so you are standing on the left side of the fridge then turn left and face the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that's to the left of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the stove then turn left and walk over to the shelves in the right corner on the wall in front of you.
Put the salt shaker on the second shelf to the left on the edge near you.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the counter with the toaster on it.
Open the cupboard that's above the left side of the coffee pot and take down the salt shaker.
Walk back over to where you put the first salt shaker.
Put the salt shaker to the right of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around then head right then left.
Grab the salt shaker in front of the cup.
Turn left then left again to reach the shelves.
Place the shaker on the middle shelf.
Turn back around and walk straight to the cabinets.
Open the leftmost cabinet and get the pepper shaker.
Turn around and head back to the shelves.
Place the pepper shaker to the right of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place the two shakers on the middle shelf.

high_descs: Move to the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the salt next to the microwave.
Bring salt to wooden rack.
Put salt on rack below the mug.
Move to the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the pepper from the cabinet above the microwave.
Bring the pepper back to the wooden rack.
Place the pepper on the shelf next to the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put the salt, pepper on the wooden rack.
